                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-1505" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES WILD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an officer. I saw the prisoner and prosecutor straggling together—I took the handkerchief out of the prisoner's trowsers—he had no pocket.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I picked it off the ground—I did not take it from the gentleman.</p>
